summary: SABR reports a narrower Q4 loss as revenues rise 3% on stronger air bookings.

headline: Palo Alto Networks Q2 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: PANW tops Q2 estimates with 27% EPS growth and lifts FY26 revenue outlook to more than $11.3B, fueled by strong Next-Gen Security and ARR momentum.
